<figure class="mw-default-size" typeof="mw:File/Thumb"><a href="/wiki/File:Rwandan_refugee_camp_in_east_Zaire.jpg" class="mw-file-description"><img src="//upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/f/f0/Rwandan_refugee_camp_in_east_Zaire.jpg/220px-Rwandan_refugee_camp_in_east_Zaire.jpg" decoding="async" width="220" height="147" class="mw-file-element" srcset="//upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/f/f0/Rwandan_refugee_camp_in_east_Zaire.jpg/330px-Rwandan_refugee_camp_in_east_Zaire.jpg 1.5x, //upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/f/f0/Rwandan_refugee_camp_in_east_Zaire.jpg/440px-Rwandan_refugee_camp_in_east_Zaire.jpg 2x" data-file-width="500" data-file-height="335" /></a><figcaption>A <a href="/wiki/Refugee_camp" title="Refugee camp">refugee camp</a> for displaced Rwandans in <a href="/wiki/Zaire" title="Zaire">Zaire</a> following the <a href="/wiki/Rwandan_genocide" title="Rwandan genocide">Rwandan genocide</a> of 1994</figcaption></figure>
